spec_data.Name: python-speaklater
spec_data.Description:
A module that provides lazy strings for translations. Basically you get an
object that appears to be a string but changes the value every time the value
is evaluated based on a callable you provide.
spec_data.Signature: RSA/SHA256, Sat 29 Jul 2017 04:14:29 AM EDT, Key ID f55e7430f5282ee4
spec_data.Summary: Implements a lazy string for python useful for use with gettext
